    <title>еңЁPythonдёӯдҪҝз”ЁC/C++вҖ”вҖ”ctypes(1)</title>
    <link href="https://lieyanqzu.github.io/blog/2018-09/python-ctypes-1/"/>
    <id>https://lieyanqzu.github.io/blog/2018-09/python-ctypes-1/</id>
    <published>2018-09-02T11:04:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-09-18T04:29:51.974Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ"><a href="#ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ" class="headerlink" title="ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ"></a>ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ</h1><blockquote><p>ctypes is a foreign function library for Python. It provides C compatible data types, and allows calling functions in DLLs or shared libraries. It can be used to wrap these libraries in pure Python.</p></blockquote><p>з®ҖеҚ•жқҘиҜҙпјҢ<code>ctypes</code>жҳҜдёҖдёӘи®©ејҖеҸ‘иҖ…еңЁPythonдёӯи°ғз”ЁC/C++еҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“зҡ„еӨ–йғЁеҮҪж•°еә“пјҢе’ҢJNIдёҖж ·пјҢдёҖиҲ¬жңүдёүз§ҚеңәжҷҜйңҖиҰҒжҲ‘д»¬еңЁPythonдёӯдҪҝз”ЁC/C++зј–еҶҷзҡ„еә“пјҡ <a id="more"></a></p><ol><li>жңүеӨ§йҮҸзҺ°еӯҳзҡ„еә“жҲ–SDKжҳҜз”ЁC/C++зј–еҶҷзҡ„пјҢеҰӮжһңжғіиҰҒеңЁPythonдёӯдҪҝз”Ёе…¶еҠҹиғҪпјҢе°ұдёҚеҫ—дёҚдҪҝз”Ё<code>ctypes</code>иҝҷж ·зҡ„еә“жқҘиҝӣиЎҢи°ғз”Ё</li><li>йңҖиҰҒдёҺPythonж ҮеҮҶеә“иҝҳжІЎжңүWrapзҡ„ж“ҚдҪңзі»з»ҹAPIдәӨдә’жҲ–иҖ…иҝӣиЎҢдёҖдәӣеә•еұӮж“ҚдҪңпјҢжҜ”еҰӮеҶ…еӯҳеҲҶй…ҚпјҲеҪ“з„¶д№ҹеҸҜд»ҘзӣҙжҺҘдҪҝз”ЁCзј–еҶҷжү©еұ•жЁЎеқ—пјҢдҪҶжҳҜ<code>ctypes</code>зҡ„дҪҝз”ЁжӣҙеҠ з®ҖеҚ•пјү</li><li>Pythonзҡ„жү§иЎҢж•ҲзҺҮеҫҲдҪҺпјҢеңЁиҝӣиЎҢи®Ўз®—еҜҶйӣҶеһӢзҡ„д»»еҠЎж—¶пјҢеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝз”ЁC/C++жқҘжҸҗй«ҳжү§иЎҢж•ҲзҺҮпјҲдҪҝз”ЁPyPyгҖҒnumbaиҝҷж ·зҡ„JITзј–иҜ‘еҷЁжқҘжҸҗй«ҳиҝҗиЎҢж•ҲзҺҮд№ҹжҳҜдёҖз§ҚйҖүжӢ©пјү</li></ol><h1 id="еҮҶеӨҮC-C-еҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“"><a href="#еҮҶеӨҮC-C-еҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“" class="headerlink" title="еҮҶеӨҮC/C++еҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“"></a>еҮҶеӨҮC/C++еҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“</h1><p>ж—ўз„¶иҰҒеңЁPythonдёӯдҪҝз”ЁеҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“пјҢйҰ–е…Ҳе°ұжқҘзңӢдёҖдёӢеҰӮдҪ•зј–еҶҷе№¶зј–иҜ‘дёҖдёӘпјҢдҪҝз”Ёзҡ„зҺҜеўғдёәmacOS 10.13пјҢзј–иҜ‘еҷЁзүҲжң¬дёәApple LLVM version 9.1.0гҖӮ</p><h2 id="extern-quot-C-quot"><a href="#extern-quot-C-quot" class="headerlink" title="extern &quot;C&quot;"></a><code>extern &quot;C&quot;</code></h2><p>еҰӮжһңжҳҜдҪҝз”ЁC++зҡ„иҜқпјҢйңҖиҰҒе°ҶеӨҙж–Үд»¶зҡ„еҮҪж•°еЈ°жҳҺеҢ…еҗ«еңЁ<code>extern &quot;C&quot;</code>дёӯпјҢиҝҷдёӘеЈ°жҳҺеңЁзј–еҶҷC++еә“зҡ„ж—¶еҖҷйқһеёёеёёз”ЁпјҢеӣ дёәC++зј–еҶҷзҡ„еә“еҫҲжңүеҸҜиғҪиў«CзЁӢеәҸдҪҝз”ЁпјҢиҖҢеңЁC++дёӯжңүзқҖеҮҪж•°йҮҚиҪҪиҝҷдёҖзү№жҖ§пјҢжүҖд»Ҙзј–иҜ‘еҗҺзҡ„ж–Үд»¶дёӯеҮҪж•°еҗҚе°ҶдјҡеҠ дёҠеҸӮж•°зұ»еһӢеҲ—иЎЁпјҢиҝҷдёӘдёҚеҗҢе°ҶеҜјиҮҙCиҜӯиЁҖе’ҢC++ж— жі•дә’зӣёи°ғз”ЁеҮҪж•°гҖӮ</p><p><code>extern &quot;C&quot;</code>еҢ…еҗ«<code>extern</code>е’Ң<code>&quot;C&quot;</code>дёӨйғЁеҲҶгҖӮ<code>extern</code>жҳҜC/C++дёӯзҡ„е…ій”®еӯ—пјҢиЎЁзӨәиў«ж Үи®°зҡ„еҸҳйҮҸжҲ–ж–№жі•еҸҜд»ҘеңЁеӨ–йғЁжЁЎеқ—иў«дҪҝз”ЁпјҢ<code>&quot;C&quot;</code>е‘ҠиҜүзј–иҜ‘еҷЁдҪҝз”ЁC-linkageиҝӣиЎҢзј–иҜ‘еЈ°жҳҺдәҶ<code>extern &quot;C&quot;</code>зҡ„д»Јз ҒгҖӮдёҖиҲ¬дјҡдҪҝз”Ёд»ҘдёӢзҡ„еӨҙж–Үд»¶жЁЎжқҝпјҡ<br><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// cpp_header.h</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">ifndef</span> __CPP_HEADER_H__</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> __CPP_HEADER_H__</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">ifdef</span> __cplusplus</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">extern</span> <span class="string">"C"</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// your cpp code here</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">ifdef</span> __cplusplus</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="cdeclе’Ң-stdcall"><a href="#cdeclе’Ң-stdcall" class="headerlink" title="__cdeclе’Ң__stdcall"></a><code>__cdecl</code>е’Ң<code>__stdcall</code></h2><p><code>__cdecl</code>жҳҜC/C++й»ҳи®Өзҡ„и°ғз”ЁзәҰе®ҡпјҢ<code>__stdcall</code>и°ғз”ЁзәҰе®ҡдёҖиҲ¬з”ЁдәҺи°ғз”ЁWin32 APIпјҢиҝҷдёӨдёӘеҮҪж•°зҡ„еҸӮж•°еҺӢж ҲйЎәеәҸжҳҜзӣёеҗҢзҡ„пјҲд»ҺеҸіеҫҖе·ҰпјүгҖӮдёӨиҖ…жңҖйҮҚиҰҒзҡ„дёҚеҗҢзӮ№еңЁдәҺжё…зҗҶе Ҷж ҲпјҢ<code>__cdecl</code>дёәи°ғз”ЁиҖ…иҙҹиҙЈжё…зҗҶе Ҷж ҲпјҢ<code>__stdcall</code>дёәиў«и°ғз”ЁиҖ…жё…зҗҶе Ҷж ҲгҖӮд№ӢжүҖд»ҘжҸҗеҲ°иҝҷдёӨз§ҚдёҚеҗҢзҡ„и°ғз”ЁзәҰе®ҡпјҢжҳҜеӣ дёәеңЁ<code>ctypes</code>дёӯеҜ№дәҺиҝҷдёӨиҖ…йңҖиҰҒCDLLе’ҢWinDLLдёӨз§ҚдёҚеҗҢзҡ„и°ғз”Ёж–№жі•жқҘеҠ иҪҪеә“гҖӮ</p><h2 id="еҰӮдҪ•зј–иҜ‘еә“"><a href="#еҰӮдҪ•зј–иҜ‘еә“" class="headerlink" title="еҰӮдҪ•зј–иҜ‘еә“"></a>еҰӮдҪ•зј–иҜ‘еә“</h2><p>еӨ§йғЁеҲҶIDEйғҪеҸҜд»Ҙж–°е»әдёҖдёӘеә“йЎ№зӣ®пјҢеңЁзј–еҶҷе®ҢжҲҗд»Јз ҒеҗҺзј–иҜ‘еҚіеҸҜеҫ—еҲ°дёҖдёӘеә“ж–Үд»¶гҖӮд№ҹеҸҜд»ҘзӣҙжҺҘдҪҝз”Ёзј–иҜ‘еҷЁзј–иҜ‘з”ҹжҲҗеә“ж–Үд»¶пјҢеҜ№дәҺ*nixж“ҚдҪңзі»з»ҹзҡ„з”ЁжҲ·пјҢеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝз”ЁgccжҲ–иҖ…clangзӯүзј–иҜ‘еҷЁпјҲWindowsз”ЁжҲ·еҲҷдёәMinGWжҲ–VCзӯүзј–иҜ‘еҷЁпјүпјҢдҪҝз”Ёд»ҘдёӢзҡ„е‘Ҫд»ӨеҚіеҸҜзј–иҜ‘з”ҹжҲҗдёҖдёӘеә“ж–Үд»¶гҖӮ<br><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gcc -shared -fPIC -o libtest.so test.c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><code>-fPIC</code>иЎЁзӨәзј–иҜ‘е°Ҷз”ҹжҲҗдҪҚзҪ®ж— е…ід»Јз ҒпјҢиҝҷиЎЁзӨәдҪҝз”Ёзј–иҜ‘еҮәзҡ„д»Јз Ғи®ҝй—®еёёйҮҸж—¶е°ҶдҪҝз”ЁGOTпјҲglobal offset table,е…ЁеұҖеҒҸз§»иЎЁпјүеҫ—еҲ°ең°еқҖгҖӮ<code>-shared</code>иЎЁзӨәзј–иҜ‘з”ҹжҲҗзҡ„еҜ№иұЎеҸҜд»Ҙиў«е…¶д»–еҸҜжү§иЎҢзЁӢеәҸе…ұдә«пјҢдёҖиҲ¬дҪҝз”Ёж—¶йңҖиҰҒеҗҢж—¶еҠ дёҠ-fPICгҖӮ</p><h1 id="ејҖе§ӢдҪҝз”Ёctypes"><a href="#ејҖе§ӢдҪҝз”Ёctypes" class="headerlink" title="ејҖе§ӢдҪҝз”Ёctypes"></a>ејҖе§ӢдҪҝз”Ёctypes</h1><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// test.c</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">hello</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"Hello, world!"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>йҰ–е…ҲеҶҷдёҖдёӘз»Ҹе…ёзҡ„HelloWorldд»Јз ҒпјҢе°Ҷд»ҘдёҠд»Јз Ғзј–иҜ‘дёәеҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“пјҢжҲ‘д»¬е°ҶеңЁPythonдёӯе°қиҜ•дҪҝз”ЁиҝҷдёӘhello()еҮҪж•°гҖӮ<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># pythonзүҲжң¬2.5+йғҪжңүctypesжЁЎеқ—</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">from</span> ctypes <span class="keyword">import</span> * <span class="comment"># еҜје…ҘctypesжЁЎеқ—</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>CDLL(<span class="string">"libtest.so"</span>).hello() <span class="comment"># зӣҙжҺҘдҪҝз”ЁеҮҪж•°еҗҚи°ғз”ЁеҮҪж•°</span></span><br><span class="line">Hello, world!</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>lib = cdll.LoadLibrary(<span class="string">'libtest.so'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>lib.hello()</span><br><span class="line">Hello, world!</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0</span> <span class="comment"># иҝ”еӣһеҖј</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>дҪҝз”Ё<code>CDLL(&quot;libxxx.so&quot;)</code>жҲ–<code>cdll.LoadLibrary(&quot;libxxx.so&quot;)</code>йғҪеҸҜд»ҘеҠ иҪҪеҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“гҖӮWindowsеҠ иҪҪdllеҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“пјҲеҰӮtest.dllпјүдёә<code>windll.test</code>жҲ–<code>cdll.test</code>пјҢеҸҜд»ҘзңҒз•Ҙ.dllеҗҺзјҖеҗҚгҖӮиҝҷйҮҢзҡ„windllз”ЁдәҺи°ғз”ЁдёҠж–ҮжҸҗеҲ°зҡ„<code>__stdcall</code>и°ғз”ЁзәҰе®ҡпјҢcdllеҲҷдёәж ҮеҮҶзҡ„<code>__cdecl</code>и°ғз”ЁзәҰе®ҡгҖӮ</p><h2 id="еҹәжң¬ж•°жҚ®зұ»еһӢ"><a href="#еҹәжң¬ж•°жҚ®зұ»еһӢ" class="headerlink" title="еҹәжң¬ж•°жҚ®зұ»еһӢ"></a>еҹәжң¬ж•°жҚ®зұ»еһӢ</h2><table><thead><tr><th>ctypes type</th><th>C type</th><th>Python type</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>c_bool</td><td>_Bool</td><td>bool (1)</td></tr><tr><td>c_char</td><td>char</td><td>1-character string</td></tr><tr><td>c_wchar</td><td>wchar_t</td><td>1-character unicode string</td></tr><tr><td>c_byte</td><td>char</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_ubyte</td><td>unsigned char</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_short</td><td>short</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_ushort</td><td>unsigned short</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_int</td><td>int</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_uint</td><td>unsigned int</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_long</td><td>long</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_ulong</td><td>unsigned long</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_longlong</td><td>__int64 or long long</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_ulonglong</td><td>unsigned __int64 or unsigned long long</td><td>int/long</td></tr><tr><td>c_float</td><td>float</td><td>float</td></tr><tr><td>c_double</td><td>double</td><td>float</td></tr><tr><td>c_longdouble</td><td>long double</td><td>float</td></tr><tr><td>c_char_p</td><td>char * (NUL terminated)</td><td>string or None</td></tr><tr><td>c_wchar_p</td><td>wchar_t * (NUL terminated)</td><td>unicode or None</td></tr><tr><td>c_void_p</td><td>void *</td><td>int/long or None</td></tr></tbody></table><p>жіЁпјҡеңЁ32дҪҚзі»з»ҹпјҢc_intжҳҜc_longзҡ„еҲ«еҗҚ</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>c_int(<span class="number">123</span>) <span class="comment"># зӣҙжҺҘдҪҝз”Ёжһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°еҲӣе»ә</span></span><br><span class="line">c_int(<span class="number">123</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>c_double(<span class="number">6.66</span>)</span><br><span class="line">c_double(<span class="number">6.66</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>ui = c_uint(<span class="number">-1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>ui</span><br><span class="line">c_uint(<span class="number">4294967295L</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>ui.value = <span class="number">1</span> <span class="comment"># еҖјеҸҜд»Ҙдҝ®ж”№</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>ui</span><br><span class="line">c_uint(<span class="number">1L</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>c_char_p</code>гҖҒ<code>c_wchar_p</code>гҖҒ<code>c_void_p</code>дҝ®ж”№еҖјзҡ„ж—¶еҖҷе°Ҷдјҡдҝ®ж”№жҢҮеҗ‘зҡ„ең°еқҖпјҢиҖҢжҢҮеҗ‘зҡ„еҶ…еӯҳеқ—жҳҜдёҚеҸҜеҸҳзҡ„пјҢиҝҷе’ҢPythonеӯ—з¬ҰдёІдёҚеҸҜеҸҳзӣёеҗҢгҖӮеҰӮжһңйңҖиҰҒдҪҝз”ЁеҸҜеҸҳеҶ…еӯҳеқ—пјҢеә”иҜҘдҪҝз”Ё<code>create_string_buffer()</code>жҲ–<code>create_unicode_buffer()</code>пјҲз”ЁдәҺwchartпјүгҖӮ</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>p = create_string_buffer(<span class="string">'Hello'</span>,<span class="number">10</span>) <span class="comment"># 10еӯ—иҠӮзҡ„еӯ—з¬ҰдёІ</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>repr(p.raw)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"'Hello\\x00\\x00\\x00\\x00\\x00'"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>p.raw = <span class="string">'Hi'</span> <span class="comment"># дёҚдјҡиҮӘеҠЁеҠ дёҠ'\0'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>repr(p.raw)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"'Hillo\\x00\\x00\\x00\\x00\\x00'"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>p.value = <span class="string">'Hi'</span> <span class="comment"># дјҡиҮӘеҠЁеҠ дёҠ'\0'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>repr(p.raw)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">"'Hi\\x00lo\\x00\\x00\\x00\\x00\\x00'"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="еҮҪж•°и°ғз”Ё"><a href="#еҮҪж•°и°ғз”Ё" class="headerlink" title="еҮҪж•°и°ғз”Ё"></a>еҮҪж•°и°ғз”Ё</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">from</span> ctypes <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>libc = CDLL(<span class="string">'libc.dylib'</span>) <span class="comment"># macOSпјҢе…¶д»–ж“ҚдҪңзі»з»ҹзҡ„libcеҗҚз§°еҸҜиғҪдёҚеҗҢ</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>libc.printf(<span class="string">"%d\n"</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>libc.printf(<span class="string">"%f\n"</span>, <span class="number">1.1</span>) <span class="comment"># ctypes.ArgumentError</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>libc.printf(<span class="string">"%f\n"</span>, c_double(<span class="number">1.1</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>ctypes</code>еҸҜд»ҘиҮӘеҠЁе°Ҷж•ҙж•°пјҲNone, integers, longsпјүгҖҒеӯ—з¬ҰдёІгҖҒunicodeеӯ—з¬ҰдёІиҪ¬жҚўдёәCж•°жҚ®зұ»еһӢпјҢжҜ”еҰӮNoneиҪ¬жҚўдёәNULLпјҢеӯ—з¬ҰдёІиҪ¬жҚўдёәеӯ—з¬ҰжҢҮй’ҲжҢҮеҗ‘зҡ„еҶ…еӯҳеқ—гҖӮдҪҶжҳҜе…¶д»–зұ»еһӢеҰӮжө®зӮ№ж•°пјҢе°ұйңҖиҰҒжҳҫејҸзҡ„еҢ…иЈ№еңЁ<code>ctypes</code>зұ»еһӢдёӯжқҘе°Ҷе®ғд»¬иҪ¬жҚўдёәCж•°жҚ®зұ»еһӢгҖӮ</p><p>еңЁеҮҪж•°и°ғз”ЁдёӯдҪҝз”ЁиҮӘе®ҡд№үзҡ„зұ»еһӢж—¶пјҢ<code>ctypes</code>е°ҶдјҡжҹҘжүҫ<code>_as_parameter_</code>еұһжҖ§дҪңдёәеҮҪж•°еҸӮж•°пјҢеҗҢж ·зҡ„пјҢиҝҷдёӘеұһжҖ§зҡ„зұ»еһӢеә”иҜҘжҳҜж•ҙж•°гҖҒеӯ—з¬ҰдёІгҖҒunicodeеӯ—з¬ҰдёІгҖӮ<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">cls</span><span class="params">(object)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">__init__</span><span class="params">(self, num)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>            self._as_parameter_ = num</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>libc.printf(<span class="string">'%d\n'</span>, cls(<span class="number">9</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">9</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="еҸӮж•°зұ»еһӢе’Ңиҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢ"><a href="#еҸӮж•°зұ»еһӢе’Ңиҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢ" class="headerlink" title="еҸӮж•°зұ»еһӢе’Ңиҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢ"></a>еҸӮж•°зұ»еһӢе’Ңиҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢ</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// test.c</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">double</span> <span class="title">divide</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">double</span> a, <span class="keyword">int</span> b)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> a / b;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>еҸҜд»Ҙз»ҷеҮҪж•°еўһеҠ дёҖдёӘ<code>argtypes</code>еұһжҖ§жқҘжҢҮе®ҡеҮҪж•°зҡ„еҸӮж•°зұ»еһӢпјҢеҪ“и°ғз”ЁеҮҪж•°ж—¶дј е…Ҙзҡ„еҸӮж•°дёҺжҢҮе®ҡеҸӮж•°зұ»еһӢдёҚдёҖиҮҙж—¶пјҢдјҡжҠӣеҮә<code>ArgumentError</code>гҖӮеҰӮжһңиҰҒе°ҶиҮӘе®ҡд№үзұ»ж”ҫеңЁ<code>argtypes</code>йҮҢйңҖиҰҒеңЁиҮӘе®ҡд№үзұ»дёӯе®һзҺ°<code>from_param()</code>ж–№жі•гҖӮ</p><p><code>ctypes</code>и°ғз”ЁеҮҪж•°ж—¶пјҢй»ҳи®Өзҡ„иҝ”еӣһеҖјжҳҜCзҡ„intзұ»еһӢпјҢеҰӮжһңжҳҜе…¶д»–иҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢиҰҒз”Ё<code>restype</code>еұһжҖ§жүӢеҠЁжҢҮе®ҡпјҢжҜ”еҰӮ<code>divide()</code>ж–№жі•зҡ„иҝ”еӣһеҖјдёә<code>double</code>зұ»еһӢпјҢе°ұиҰҒз»ҷ<code>restype</code>иөӢеҖјдёҖдёӘ<code>c_double</code>гҖӮеҰӮжһңиҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢжҳҜж•ҙж•°пјҢиҝҳеҸҜд»Ҙз»ҷ<code>restype</code>иөӢеҖјдёҖдёӘcallableеҜ№иұЎпјҢеҮҪж•°иҝ”еӣһеҖје°ҶдјҡдҪңдёәеҸӮж•°дј з»ҷcallableеҜ№иұЎпјҢиҝҷз§Қз”Ёжі•еңЁжЈҖжөӢеҮҪж•°и°ғз”ЁеҮәй”ҷж—¶еҫҲжңүз”ЁгҖӮ</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> ctypes <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">num</span><span class="params">(object)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">from_param</span><span class="params">(param)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> type(param) == num: <span class="comment"># type check</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> param <span class="comment"># return object itself</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">raise</span> TypeError(<span class="string">'wrong type'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">__init__</span><span class="params">(self, n)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        self._as_parameter_ = n</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">divide = CDLL(<span class="string">'libtest.so'</span>).divide</span><br><span class="line">divide.argtypes = [c_double, num] <span class="comment"># list</span></span><br><span class="line">divide.restype = c_double</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> divide(<span class="number">0.5</span>, num(<span class="number">2</span>)) <span class="comment"># print: 0.25</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">well_hello</span><span class="params">(val)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> val == <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"wonderful hello"</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"bad hello"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hello = CDLL(<span class="string">'libtest.so'</span>).hello</span><br><span class="line">hello.restype = well_hello</span><br><span class="line">hello() <span class="comment"># print: Hello, world!wonderful hello</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="еӨҚеҗҲзұ»еһӢзҡ„дҪҝз”Ё"><a href="#еӨҚеҗҲзұ»еһӢзҡ„дҪҝз”Ё" class="headerlink" title="еӨҚеҗҲзұ»еһӢзҡ„дҪҝз”Ё"></a>еӨҚеҗҲзұ»еһӢзҡ„дҪҝз”Ё</h2><p>дёӢзҜҮз»§з»ӯ</p><h1 id="еҸӮиҖғ"><a href="#еҸӮиҖғ" class="headerlink" title="еҸӮиҖғ"></a>еҸӮиҖғ</h1><ol><li><a href="https://docs.python.org/2/library/ctypes.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">15.17. ctypes вҖ” A foreign function library for Python</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h1 id=&quot;ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;ctypesжҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ctypes is a foreign function library for Python. It provides C compatible data types, and allows calling functions in DLLs or shared libraries. It can be used to wrap these libraries in pure Python.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;з®ҖеҚ•жқҘиҜҙпјҢ&lt;code&gt;ctypes&lt;/code&gt;жҳҜдёҖдёӘи®©ејҖеҸ‘иҖ…еңЁPythonдёӯи°ғз”ЁC/C++еҠЁжҖҒй“ҫжҺҘеә“зҡ„еӨ–йғЁеҮҪж•°еә“пјҢе’ҢJNIдёҖж ·пјҢдёҖиҲ¬жңүдёүз§ҚеңәжҷҜйңҖиҰҒжҲ‘д»¬еңЁPythonдёӯдҪҝз”ЁC/C++зј–еҶҷзҡ„еә“пјҡ
    
    </summary>
    
