    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Classзұ»жҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ"><a href="#Classзұ»жҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ" class="headerlink" title="Classзұ»жҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ"></a>Classзұ»жҳҜд»Җд№Ҳ</h1><p>йҖҡиҝҮ<code>Class</code>зұ»зҡ„ж–ҮжЎЈд»Ӣз»ҚеҸҜд»Ҙеҫ—зҹҘд»ҘдёӢеҮ зӮ№пјҡ</p><ul><li><code>Class</code>зұ»зҡ„е®һдҫӢд»ЈиЎЁдәҶжӯЈеңЁиҝҗиЎҢзҡ„Javaеә”з”Ёзҡ„зұ»дёҺжҺҘеҸЈ</li><li>жһҡдёҫжҳҜдёҖз§Қзұ»пјҢжіЁи§ЈжҳҜдёҖз§ҚжҺҘеҸЈ <a id="more"></a></li><li><p>жҜҸдёӘж•°з»„д№ҹйғҪеұһдәҺдёҖдёӘзұ»пјҢиҝҷдёӘ<code>Class</code>еҜ№иұЎиў«жүҖжңүе…·жңүзӣёеҗҢе…ғзҙ зұ»еһӢе’Ңз»ҙж•°зҡ„ж•°з»„е…ұдә«</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a[] = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[<span class="number">3</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b[] = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>[<span class="number">4</span>];</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(a.getClass() == b.getClass()); <span class="comment">// true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>еҺҹз”ҹJavaзұ»еһӢ(<code>boolean</code>, <code>byte</code>, <code>char</code>, <code>short</code>, <code>int</code>, <code>long</code>, <code>float</code>, and <code>double</code>)д»ҘеҸҠ<code>void</code>еҗҢж ·жҳҜ<code>Class</code>еҜ№иұЎ</p></li><li><code>Class</code>зұ»жІЎжңүе…¬жңүжһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°пјҢиҖҢжҳҜз”ұJVMиҮӘеҠЁи°ғз”Ёзұ»еҠ иҪҪеҷЁзҡ„<code>defineClass</code>ж–№жі•</li></ul><h2 id="иҺ·еҫ—ClassеҜ№иұЎзҡ„ж–№жі•"><a href="#иҺ·еҫ—ClassеҜ№иұЎзҡ„ж–№жі•" class="headerlink" title="иҺ·еҫ—ClassеҜ№иұЎзҡ„ж–№жі•"></a>иҺ·еҫ—ClassеҜ№иұЎзҡ„ж–№жі•</h2><ol><li>зӣҙжҺҘдҪҝз”Ёзұ»еҗҚ+.classпјҢеҰӮ<code>String.class</code></li><li><p>иҝҗиЎҢж—¶йҖҡиҝҮзұ»еҗҚиҺ·еҫ—пјҢйңҖиҰҒеҢ…жӢ¬еҢ…еҗҚзҡ„зұ»е…ЁеҗҚпјҢеҰӮжһңжүҫдёҚеҲ°зұ»дјҡжҠӣеҮә<code>ClassNotFoundException</code></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">String className = <span class="string">"java.lang.String"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">Class&lt;?&gt; clazz = Class.forName(className);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>дҪҝз”Ё<code>Object</code>зҡ„<code>getClass</code>ж–№жі•</p></li></ol><h2 id="дҪҝз”ЁClass-lt-gt"><a href="#дҪҝз”ЁClass-lt-gt" class="headerlink" title="дҪҝз”ЁClass&lt;?&gt;"></a>дҪҝз”ЁClass&lt;?&gt;</h2><p><code>Class</code>зұ»жҳҜжіӣеһӢзұ»пјҢдҪҝз”Ёж—¶еҸҜд»ҘжҢҮе®ҡзұ»еһӢ<code>T</code>пјҢеҜ№дәҺ<code>Class</code>зұ»еӨ§еӨҡж•°жғ…еҶөдҪҝз”ЁйҖҡй…Қз¬Ұ<code>?</code>жқҘиЎЁзӨәжҺҘеҸ—д»»дҪ•зұ»еһӢгҖӮ<br><code>Class clazz</code>е’Ң<code>Class&lt;?&gt; clazz</code>еңЁдҪҝз”ЁдёҠжІЎжңүеҢәеҲ«пјҢеӣ дёәзј–иҜ‘еҷЁдјҡиҮӘеҠЁжҺЁжөӢпјҢдҪҶжҳҜжҳҫејҸеҶҷжҳҺжіӣеһӢзұ»еһӢеҸҜд»Ҙеўһејәд»Јз ҒеҸҜиҜ»жҖ§гҖӮ</p><p>Bruce Eckel, Thinking in Java:</p><blockquote><p>In Java SE5, Class&lt;?&gt; is preferred over plain Class, even though they are equivalent and the plain Class, as you saw, doesnвҖҷt produce a compiler warning. The benefit of Class&lt;?&gt; is that it indicates that you arenвҖҷt just using a non-specific class reference by accident, or out of ignorance. You chose the non-specific version.</p></blockquote><h1 id="еёёз”Ёж–№жі•"><a href="#еёёз”Ёж–№жі•" class="headerlink" title="еёёз”Ёж–№жі•"></a>еёёз”Ёж–№жі•</h1><h2 id="йқҷжҖҒж–№жі•"><a href="#йқҷжҖҒж–№жі•" class="headerlink" title="йқҷжҖҒж–№жі•"></a>йқҷжҖҒж–№жі•</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> Class&lt;?&gt; forName(String className)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> Class&lt;?&gt; forName(String name, <span class="keyword">boolean</span> initialize, ClassLoader loader)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>йҖҡиҝҮзұ»еҗҚиҺ·еҫ—зұ»еҜ№иұЎпјҢеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝз”Ёз»ҷе®ҡзҡ„зұ»еҠ иҪҪеҷЁгҖӮж•°з»„зҡ„зұ»еҗҚжҳҜ<code>[Lзұ»еҗҚ;</code>(жіЁж„ҸжңүдёӘеҲҶеҸ·)пјҢеҺҹз”ҹзұ»еһӢдёә<code>[I</code>(int[]),<code>[B</code>(byte[]),<code>[Z</code>(boolean[]),<code>[C</code>(char[]),<code>[D</code>(double[]),<code>[F</code>(float[]),<code>[J</code>(long[]),<code>[S</code>(short[])пјҢеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝз”Ё<code>getComponentType</code>ж–№жі•иҺ·еҫ—е…ғзҙ зұ»еһӢгҖӮ</p><h2 id="е…¬жңүж–№жі•"><a href="#е…¬жңүж–№жі•" class="headerlink" title="е…¬жңүж–№жі•"></a>е…¬жңүж–№жі•</h2><h3 id="е®һдҫӢ"><a href="#е®һдҫӢ" class="headerlink" title="е®һдҫӢ"></a>е®һдҫӢ</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> T <span class="title">newInstance</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">              <span class="keyword">throws</span> InstantiationException,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">                     IllegalAccessException</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>еҲӣе»әдёҖдёӘзұ»зҡ„е®һдҫӢеҜ№иұЎпјҢиҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢжҳҜжіӣеһӢзұ»еһӢ<br><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">isInstance</span><span class="params">(Object obj)</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>зӣёеҪ“дәҺе…ій”®еӯ—<code>instanceof</code>зҡ„еҠЁжҖҒе®һзҺ°</p><h3 id="ж–№жі•-amp-жһ„йҖ еҷЁ-amp-еӯ—ж®ө"><a href="#ж–№жі•-amp-жһ„йҖ еҷЁ-amp-еӯ—ж®ө" class="headerlink" title="ж–№жі•&amp;жһ„йҖ еҷЁ&amp;еӯ—ж®ө"></a>ж–№жі•&amp;жһ„йҖ еҷЁ&amp;еӯ—ж®ө</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Method</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Method <span class="title">getMethod</span><span class="params">(String name,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">                        Class&lt;?&gt;... parameterTypes)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">                 <span class="keyword">throws</span> NoSuchMethodException,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">                        SecurityException</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Method <span class="title">getDeclaredMethod</span><span class="params">(String name,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">                                Class&lt;?&gt;... parameterTypes)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">                         <span class="keyword">throws</span> NoSuchMethodException,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">                                SecurityException</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Method[] <span class="title">getMethods</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">                    <span class="keyword">throws</span> SecurityException</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Method[] <span class="title">getDeclaredMethods</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">                            <span class="keyword">throws</span> SecurityException</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Methodз»“е°ҫзҡ„ж–№жі•йҖҡиҝҮжҢҮе®ҡзҡ„ж–№жі•еҗҚе’ҢеҸӮж•°еҲ—иЎЁеҸҚе°„еҫ—еҲ°ж–№жі•пјҢMethodsзӣҙжҺҘеҫ—еҲ°зұ»зҡ„жүҖжңүж–№жі•гҖӮеёҰжңүDeclaredзҡ„ж–№жі•еҸҜд»ҘиҺ·еҸ–еҲ°жүҖжңүеӣӣз§Қи®ҝй—®зұ»еһӢзҡ„ж–№жі•пјҢдҪҶдёҚеҢ…еҗ«з»§жүҝзҡ„ж–№жі•пјҢдёҚеёҰDecleardзҡ„ж–№жі•еҸӘеҸҜд»ҘиҺ·еҫ—зұ»зҡ„е…¬жңүж–№жі•пјҢеҢ…еҗ«з»§жүҝиҖҢжқҘзҡ„ж–№жі•гҖӮ<br>еҗҢж—¶пјҢжһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°ж–№жі•е’Ңеӯ—ж®өд№ҹжңүзқҖзұ»дјјзҡ„APIгҖӮ<br><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Field</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Field <span class="title">getField</span><span class="params">(String name)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Field <span class="title">getDeclaredField</span><span class="params">(String name)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Field[]<span class="title">getFields</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Field[]<span class="title">getDeclaredFields</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="comment">// Constructor</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Constructor&lt;T&gt; <span class="title">getConstructor</span><span class="params">(Class&lt;?&gt;... parameterTypes)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Constructor&lt;T&gt; <span class="title">getDeclaredConstructor</span><span class="params">(Class&lt;?&gt;... parameterTypes)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Constructor&lt;?&gt;[] <span class="title">getConstructors</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Constructor&lt;?&gt;[] <span class="title">getDeclaredConstructors</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h4 id="Methodзұ»"><a href="#Methodзұ»" class="headerlink" title="Methodзұ»"></a>Methodзұ»</h4><p>Methodзұ»е°ҒиЈ…дәҶзұ»ж–№жі•зҡ„дёҖзі»еҲ—дҝЎжҒҜпјҢе№¶дё”еҸҜд»ҘйҖҡиҝҮ<code>invoke</code>ж–№жі•и°ғз”ЁгҖӮ</p><h4 id="Constructorзұ»"><a href="#Constructorзұ»" class="headerlink" title="Constructorзұ»"></a>Constructorзұ»</h4><p>Constructorзұ»е°ҒиЈ…дәҶзұ»жһ„йҖ еҷЁзҡ„дёҖзі»еҲ—дҝЎжҒҜпјҢе№¶дё”еҸҜд»ҘйҖҡиҝҮ<code>newInstance</code>ж–№жі•и°ғз”ЁгҖӮ</p><h4 id="Fieldзұ»"><a href="#Fieldзұ»" class="headerlink" title="Fieldзұ»"></a>Fieldзұ»</h4><p>Fieldзұ»е°ҒиЈ…дәҶзұ»еӯ—ж®өзҡ„дёҖзі»еҲ—дҝЎжҒҜпјҢе№¶дё”еҸҜд»ҘйҖҡиҝҮ<code>get</code>е’Ң<code>set</code>ж–№жі•иҺ·еҸ–/и®ҫзҪ®еҸҳйҮҸеҖјгҖӮ</p><h3 id="жіЁи§Ј"><a href="#жіЁи§Ј" class="headerlink" title="жіЁи§Ј"></a>жіЁи§Ј</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;A extends Annotation&gt; <span class="function">A <span class="title">getAnnotation</span><span class="params">(Class&lt;A&gt; annotationClass)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">&lt;A extends Annotation&gt; A <span class="title">getDeclaredAnnotation</span><span class="params">(Class&lt;A&gt; annotationClass)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Annotation[] <span class="title">getAnnotations</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Annotation[] <span class="title">getDeclaredAnnotations</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">&lt;A extends Annotation&gt; A[] <span class="title">getAnnotationsByType</span><span class="params">(Class&lt;A&gt; annotationClass)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">&lt;A extends Annotation&gt; A[] <span class="title">getDeclaredAnnotationsByType</span><span class="params">(Class&lt;A&gt; annotationClass)</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>иҝ”еӣһзұ»зҡ„жіЁи§ЈпјҢеүҚеӣӣдёӘж–№жі•дёҺеүҚйқўзҡ„getж–№жі•зұ»дјјпјҢж ҮжңүDeclaredзҡ„ж–№жі•еҸҜд»Ҙеҫ—еҲ°з»§жүҝиҖҢжқҘзҡ„жіЁи§ЈпјҢд»ҘByTypeз»“е°ҫзҡ„ж–№жі•жҳҜз”ЁжқҘиҺ·еҫ—еҸҜйҮҚеӨҚжіЁи§Јзҡ„жіЁи§Јж•°з»„гҖӮ</p><h3 id="TypeжҺҘеҸЈ"><a href="#TypeжҺҘеҸЈ" class="headerlink" title="TypeжҺҘеҸЈ"></a>TypeжҺҘеҸЈ</h3><p>TypeжҳҜJavaдёӯжүҖжңүзұ»еһӢзҡ„йҖҡз”ЁзҲ¶жҺҘеҸЈпјҢеҢ…жӢ¬raw types(еҺҹе§Ӣзұ»еһӢпјҢдёҚеҗ«зұ»еһӢеҸҳйҮҸзҡ„жіӣеһӢеЈ°жҳҺ), parameterized types(еҸӮж•°еҢ–зұ»еһӢпјҢзӣёеҪ“дәҺжіӣеһӢ), array types(ж•°з»„зұ»еһӢ), type variables(зұ»еһӢеҸҳйҮҸпјҢжҢҮ<code>class name&lt;T1, T2, ..., Tn&gt;</code>дёӯзҡ„<code>T1</code>пјҢ<code>T2</code>зӯү) and primitive types(еҺҹз”ҹзұ»еһӢ)гҖӮ<br>иҝҷдёӘжҺҘеҸЈеҸӘжңүдёҖдёӘж–№жі•<code>getTypeName</code>гҖӮ</p><h3 id="зҲ¶зұ»-amp-жҺҘеҸЈ"><a href="#зҲ¶зұ»-amp-жҺҘеҸЈ" class="headerlink" title="зҲ¶зұ»&amp;жҺҘеҸЈ"></a>зҲ¶зұ»&amp;жҺҘеҸЈ</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Class&lt;?&gt;[]getInterfaces()</span><br><span class="line">Class&lt;? <span class="keyword">super</span> T&gt; getSuperclass()</span><br><span class="line">Type[] getGenericInterfaces()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Type <span class="title">getGenericSuperclass</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> AnnotatedType[] <span class="title">getAnnotatedInterfaces</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> AnnotatedType <span class="title">getAnnotatedSuperclass</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>getGenericзі»еҲ—ж–№жі•иҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢдёәTypeпјҢдёҖиҲ¬дёәParameterizedTypeпјҢз”ЁдәҺзҲ¶зұ»дёәжіӣеһӢзұ»зҡ„жғ…еҶөгҖӮ<br>getAnnotatedзі»еҲ—ж–№жі•иҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢдёәAnnotatedTypeпјҢз”ЁдәҺз»§жүҝзҲ¶зұ»ж—¶дҪҝз”ЁдәҶжіЁи§Јзҡ„жғ…еҶөпјҢйҖҡиҝҮ<code>getAnnotatedSuperclass().getAnnotations()</code>иҺ·еҫ—жіЁи§Јж•°з»„гҖӮ</p><h1 id="е®һйҷ…дҪҝз”Ё"><a href="#е®һйҷ…дҪҝз”Ё" class="headerlink" title="е®һйҷ…дҪҝз”Ё"></a>е®һйҷ…дҪҝз”Ё</h1><p>дҪҝз”ЁJavaзҡ„еҸҚе°„жңәеҲ¶еҸҜд»ҘеңЁиҝҗиЎҢж—¶еҠЁжҖҒзҡ„е®һзҺ°ж–№жі•пјҢдҪҝз”Ё<code>Proxy.newProxyInstance()</code>ж–№жі•жқҘеҲӣе»әеҠЁжҖҒд»ЈзҗҶпјҢйҖҡиҝҮе®һзҺ°<code>InvocationHandler</code>жҺҘеҸЈпјҢе°ҶеҜ№proxyзҡ„и°ғз”ЁиҪ¬з§»еҲ°handlerдёҠгҖӮ<br>д»ҘдёҖдёӘNo-Op ProxyдҪңдёәдҫӢеӯҗ<br><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">NoOpProxy</span>&lt;<span class="title">T</span>&gt; <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">InvocationHandler</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> WeakReference&lt;T&gt; obj;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@SuppressWarnings</span>(<span class="string">"unchecked"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> T <span class="title">bind</span><span class="params">(T obj)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">this</span>.obj = <span class="keyword">new</span> WeakReference&lt;&gt;(obj);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> (T) Proxy.newProxyInstance(obj.getClass().getClassLoader(),</span><br><span class="line">                obj.getClass().getInterfaces(), <span class="keyword">this</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Object <span class="title">invoke</span><span class="params">(Object proxy, Method method, Object[] args)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> Throwable </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (obj == <span class="keyword">null</span> || obj.get() == <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> method.invoke(obj.get(), args);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>е°ҶйңҖиҰҒзҡ„еҜ№иұЎеӯҳеңЁ<code>Proxy</code>йҮҢзҡ„<code>WeakReference</code>дёӯпјҢеңЁи°ғз”Ёж–№жі•д№ӢеүҚз”ұд»ЈзҗҶжқҘеҲӨж–ӯеҜ№иұЎжҳҜеҗҰе·Іиў«еӣһж”¶пјҢиӢҘжІЎжңүиў«еӣһж”¶е°ұи°ғз”Ёзӣёеә”ж–№жі•пјҢиҝҷж ·еңЁдҪҝз”Ё<code>WeakReference</code>ж—¶е°ұдёҚйңҖиҰҒдёҚж–ӯеңЁд»Јз ҒйҮҢеҶҷnull checkпјҢеҪ“з„¶еҸҚе°„зҡ„дҪҝз”ЁдјҡдҪҝж•ҲзҺҮйҷҚдҪҺгҖӮ</p><h1 id="еҸӮиҖғ"><a href="#еҸӮиҖғ" class="headerlink" title="еҸӮиҖғ"></a>еҸӮиҖғ</h1><ol><li><a href="https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Class.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Class (Java Platform SE 8 )</a></li><li><a href="http://tutorials.jenkov.com/java-reflection/annotations.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Java Reflection - Annotations</a></li><li><a href="https://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se8/html/jls-4.html#jls-4.8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chapter 4. Types, Values, and Variables/JLS 4.8 Raw Types</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
